{"_path":"/maps/_architecture","_dir":"maps","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"架构设计","description":"架构设计是指软件系统的整体结构，它包括软件元素、元素之间的关系以及元素外部可见的属性。架构设计是软件设计的重要组成部分，它是软件设计的第一个阶段，也是软件设计的核心。","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"quick-questions"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Quick Questions"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"如何储存用户密码"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"如何储存用户密码？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"除开双因素认证等鉴权方式，单看用户密码的落库。一般人都知道不能明文存储，但是简单的加密也并不安全：MD5、SHA-1、SHA-256 等哈希算法，都可以通过彩虹表等方式破解。所以，一般会选择加盐哈希算法，比如 bcrypt、scrypt，并采用多层加密策略。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"加盐过程有哪些容易出现的错误"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"加盐过程有哪些容易出现的错误？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"盐太短或重复使用都会导致问题，此外，应该使用安全的随机函数生成盐，如 C/C++ 的 "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"CryptGenRandom"}]},{"type":"text","value":"。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"什么是-password-hashing"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"什么是 Password Hashing？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"加盐哈希在现代计算机来看已经不够安全，Password Hashing 应当能应付以下几种攻击："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"加密算法破解（原值还原、哈希碰撞等）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"查表、彩虹表"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"CPU 优化攻击"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"GPU、FPGA、ASIC 等专用硬件攻击"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"旁路攻击：通过检测电磁波、功耗等信息来推算信息"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.cnblogs.com/xinzhao/p/6035847.html","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"用户密码加密存储十问十答，一文说透密码安全存储"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"dropbox-的密码存储策略是什么"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Dropbox 的密码存储策略是什么？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"将用户密码使用 sha256 归一化，因为 bcrypt 的结果对长度敏感"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"使用 bcrypt 每用户加盐加密"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"使用 AES256 全局加密，并使用专用的硬件及定期更换策略等"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"此外，Dropbox 表示也在关注 Argon2 等竞赛新秀。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://dropbox.tech/security/how-dropbox-securely-stores-your-passwords","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"How Dropbox securely stores your passwords"}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"quick-questions","depth":2,"text":"Quick Questions"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_architecture:index.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_architecture/index.md","_stem":"6.maps/_architecture/index","_extension":"md"}